    "updated_at": "2023-12-31T21:04:38Z",
    "body": "While i can strongly recommend direnv for project setups per dir, you can get the same effect with a \"cd\" function in your bashrc/zshrc which would first check on which dir you are and then either set or unset the end var and then call \"builtin cd\". Or if you are in zsh with a precmd function.",
